css
a {
transition: color 1s linear;
}
The values that the transition property accepts are, in order, the property that the transition is applied to, the duration of the transition, and then the timing If there are multiple properties that have a transition, you can write the values for each separated by a comma:
css
p {
transition: property1 0 1s, property2 0 6s linear;
}
